<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, user-scalable=no" />
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no, address=no, email=no" />
    <meta name="format-detection" content="no" />

    <title>다이어트 Farm 로그인</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        @media screen and (min-width:360px)and (max-width:1079px) {.web_repwdchange{display:none}}
        @media screen and (min-width:1080px){.mobile_repwdchange{display:none} }
        </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/signup.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style02.css">
    <%-include('general/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="web_repwdchange">
        <%-include('general/header_web') %>   
    </div>
    <div class="mobile_repwdChange">
        <section class="detail_title">
            <h2>비밀번호 재설정</h2>
            <script type="text/javascript">
                function goBack() {
                    window.history.back();
                }
            </script>
            <div class="btnback"><a href="#" value="취소" onclick="goBack()"><img src="images/leftarrow_ico_my.png" alt="" style="left:10px;margin-top:-5px"> </a>
            </div>
        </section>
        </div><!--//mobile_repwdChange-->
        <main id="content" class="content_newPwd">
            <div class="new_pwd">
             <h3>새 비밀번호</h3>
             <input type="password" placeholder="새 비밀번호를 입력해주세요">
             <p>- 10자 이상 입력</p>
             <p>- 영문/숫자/특수문자 2개 이상 조합</p>
             </div>
             <div class="new_pwd_ck">
             <h3>새 비밀번호 확인</h3>
             <input type="password" placeholder="새 비밀번호를 한번 더 입력해주세요">
             <p>- 동일한 비밀번호를 입력해주세요</p>
             </div>
             <p class="red_sign">비밀번호를 변경하려면 PC, PC Player, 모바일 웹/APP에 로그인 되어 있는 모든 계정이 로그아웃 됩니다.</p>
             <div class="btn_area_pwd">
                 <button type="button" id="btnPwdChange">
                     비밀번호 변경
                 </button>
             </div>
         </main>
    <script src="signup.js"></script>
</body></html>